      public void start​(javafx.stage.Stage primaryStage) throws java.lang.Exception
      The methods used to represent the entry point of Application and setting up the primary stage for this application

      Specified by:
      start in class javafx.application.Application
      Parameters:
      primaryStage - the primary stage for this application, onto which the application scene can be set. Applications may create other stages, if needed, but they will not be primary stages.

      java.lang.Exception - When fails to construct the GUI.
